# `insta` snapshot directory.
#
# Scaffold landed in PR 4a (#5); first real snapshot lands PR 4b (golden
# `insta::assert_json_snapshot!` over the deserialized fixture manifest)
# or PR 8b (golden `insta::assert_snapshot!` over the rendered HTML).
#
# Snapshots are committed (`.snap` files) and reviewed with `cargo insta
# review` / `cargo insta accept`. The `*.snap.new` pending-snapshot
# artifacts are gitignored at the repo root.
